metadata.description: the bug character, who has a dark and mysterious world, is an arms dealer in this story. he takes his place at the very entrance of the market place. you can see both outdoor environmental forms and indoor forms at the same time.. мцппфр is this piece that I drew when I was learning Russian, it's a word I derived myself. it doesn't mean anything exactly.
